{"tid":1060354,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇好鍾意Desert Boot嘅巴絲？","createTime":"2019-03-13T17:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T14:33:57.000Z","uid":227650,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"279e09b8c76bc99a384d11ed718ef90f27b46c75","tid":1060354,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"呢對鞋夠曬百搭，襯牛仔褲得、chino得;甚至短褲都得。我最鍾意係佢斯文得嚟又帶點粗曠嘅感覺， 其他有呢種感覺嘅鞋只係諗到chelsea boots、chukka boots同埋red wing某啲型號。<br />\n<br />\nDesert Boot有好多隻色:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/14/001311_10b081f2aaf5bc5372f1703fe48bedfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F001311_10b081f2aaf5bc5372f1703fe48bedfb.jpg&h=1414d49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襯牛:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/14/001325_1b8ff8b565a854ca95ebded71fa2ce7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F001325_1b8ff8b565a854ca95ebded71fa2ce7e.jpg&h=e56a61dd&s={SIZE}\" />襯卡其色chino:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/14/001416_b2ff684df735d06a4378ec169ae23936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F001416_b2ff684df735d06a4378ec169ae23936.jpg&h=ab4acb1d&s={SIZE}\" />甚至短褲:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/14/001603_db123f1336f732dc2618485cbe201a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F14%2F001603_db123f1336f732dc2618485cbe201a3c.jpg&h=fbd8212b&s={SIZE}\" />不過對我嚟講夏天盡量著返波鞋<br />\n<br />\n但都有缺點㗎，就係有機會成日要換底。<br />\n<br />\nBtw,一講起Desert Boot，好似總係諗起Clarks"},{"pid":"be420f9d91c65c119ba8fc08b79f37dc64929f9b","tid":1060354,"uid":143546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"襯短褲不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 